Product Description


About Squishmallows

Squishmallows plush toys are here to fill your hearts with love and affection. Since 2017, the versatile Squishmallows have grown into an international phenomenon and offer comfort, support and more. Squishmallows come in a variety of sizes, animals, and colors with unique bios to cuddle, collect, gift, and even use as a pillow.

Squishmallows 5" Plush Mystery Box

Collect them all!

A Squishtastic surprise! The Squishmallow Mystery Box contains five squishy and soft plush! Features fun and cute 5" styles chosen randomly! Collect all 10! These super soft, collectible plush toys make great cuddle companions! Makes a great gift for kids who love stuffed animals! The assorted set is also perfect for stocking stuffers and party favors!

  • Authentic 5" Squishmallows
  • Exclusive Squishmallows Mystery Box
  • Machine washable and dryable
  • Join the Squad! Please visit our Amazon brand store for all the latest and greatest Squish

ADORABLE PLUSH

Squishmallows are made of high quality and marshmallow soft materials. These super soft, collectible plush toys make great cuddle companions! Makes a great gift for kids who love stuffed animals! The assorted set is also perfect for stocking stuffers, Easter basket stuffers and party favors!

CUDDLE, SQUEEZE, AND PLAY

Authentic Squishmallows are made with high quality and marshmallow-soft materials, making them the cutest and softest plush around. Squeeze, cuddle, and play with your Squishmellows everywhere. Squishmallows are perfect for boys and girls of all ages.

JOIN THE SQUAD

Grow your Squshmallow Squad with more adorable, collectible, and obsessable plush.

Squishmallows come in a variety of sizes.

Add your favorite characters and animals to your collection today. Please visit our Amazon brand store for all the latest and greatest Squish.

About Jazwares

Jazwares, a subsidiary of Alleghany Capital Corporation, specializes in consumer products including toys, plush, action figures, collectibles and musical instruments. Jazwares portfolio includes a variety of dynamic licensed and wholly owned brands. With over 20 years of design, development, and manufacturing experience, Jazwares is a company with a progressive focus on identifying new trends and transforming them into high-quality products for consumers of all ages.

Jazwares, which is headquartered in Sunrise, FL, has offices around the world and sells in over 100 countries. Since its inception in 1997, Jazwares continues to grow through the development of new products and the strategic acquisitions of companies like First Act, Russ Berrie, Zag Toys, Wicked Cool Toys and Kellytoy.

      How customer reviews and ratings work

      Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

      To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
